707321f-a.text:

707324f-a.title: Brooklyn: Water St. - Dock St.
707324f-a.text:
Water Street, south side, east from Dock Street. At the right
in order standing is the Hamilton and Sons Foundry Bldg. and the
Sweeny Mfg. Co. Bldg. In the left backaround is the 12 story Gair
Building.
April 4, 1938.
